				<div class="pum-content popmake-content" tabindex="0">
			<ol start="1" type="1">
<li>Association of Indian Universities <a href="https://www.einnews.com/pr_news/635327951/association-of-indian-universities-aiu-india-signs-mou-with-edify-online-usa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.einnews.com/pr_news/635327951/association-of-indian-universities-aiu-india-signs-mou-with-edify-online-usa&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1764133573902000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3Z-PpaKczhEXdQkqNcM_AI">(AIU), India, Signs MoU with Edify Online, USA</a>, May 23, 2023.<u></u><u></u></li>
<li><a href="https://www.einpresswire.com/article/789942511/unveiled-internationalizing-higher-education-report-a-study-of-preparedness-of-indian-higher-education-institutions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.einpresswire.com/article/789942511/unveiled-internationalizing-higher-education-report-a-study-of-preparedness-of-indian-higher-education-institutions&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1764133573902000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0iTL66-wCs1t1nhS3WkGlG">IHE Report was unveiled</a>, by Secretary General, Dr. Mittal, Vik Agarwal, and others, on February 2025.<u></u><u></u></li>
<li><a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1x3Bam5yo6VNURHuubwkms2k_1FctWAry/view?usp=drive_link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://drive.google.com/file/d/1x3Bam5yo6VNURHuubwkms2k_1FctWAry/view?usp%3Ddrive_link&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1764133573902000&amp;usg=AOvVaw3NQAVChShWk6zk0n-dsrb5">Vik’s video at Amity</a> at the 99<sup>th</sup> annual AIU general meet and conference of VCs, on June 23, 2025 &#8211; plan to launch university clusters initiative with ‘Shared HEIs Ecosystem’ framework.  <u></u><u></u></li>
</ol>
